name: The Sandman and His Ruby Slippers
description: Part 2 in my digital series inspired by Rorschach Art will consist of 3 unique pieces created from the same canvas. In part 2 I experimented with folding the original image off center and mirroring random angles with editing. Please visit my blog for more information on my process. https://beta.cent.co/FlowerP0wer (2.1-The Sandman and His Ruby Slippers,2.2-Third Eye Third Mind & The Moons Between Us,2.3-The Oculus Shapeshifter)
